{"tid":742821,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"喺日本生針眼點樣處理好？","createTime":"2018-07-15T01:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T09:30:21.000Z","uid":84257,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"87010e67f82b9405c08f74716d453e39ecc7e59c","tid":742821,"uid":84257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T01:53:23.000Z","msg":"請問一下日本藥妝店有無賣非處方眼用消炎藥膏？<br />\n琴日朝早覺得眼痛，之後check住發現眼頭有少少紅，禁咗下發現會有少少雜質(膿?)會流出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放心我check完無再擠佢<br />\n嚟緊決定唔帶con唔化眼妝，但係怕佢會發炎感染唔自己好。<br />\n18先番香港，想問問有無巴絲可以提供意見教我儘早處理初期眼瘡。<br />\n香港無點生過眼瘡，真係唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa595391c6c7967b7434fd2652154ec46ac900a9","tid":742821,"uid":5448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"買啲殺菌眼藥水試試先<br />\n唔得就睇醫生返香港再claim旅遊保險"},{"pid":"76eaae53b17d3482a04995cba3ef4402cf3d7e09","tid":742821,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"唔係擠哂出嚟就冇事嫁啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecbced9cde0785c84d42a7335011d12740bc415","tid":742821,"uid":84257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa595391c6c7967b7434fd2652154ec46ac900a9","tid":742821,"uid":5448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"買啲殺菌眼藥水試試先<br />\n唔得就睇醫生返香港再claim旅遊保險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"search咗ロート抗菌目薬ｉ好似可以治療麥粒腫，唔知好唔好洗<br />\n但係旅遊保險好似全部都要求第一次醫生要喺日本睇咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c19c28838fe3865ca35ffcb3c77a8786b11269","tid":742821,"uid":84257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76eaae53b17d3482a04995cba3ef4402cf3d7e09","tid":742821,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T02:43:38.000Z","msg":"唔係擠哂出嚟就冇事嫁啦咩<img src